Package: DPdii
Type: Package
Title: Data Paching Technique Using Delete - Impute Iteration 
Version: 0.0.1.1
Author: person("Koji", "Toda", email="toda@fit.ac.jp",role=c("aut","cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <toda@fit.ac.jp>
Description: Data Patching using deletion-imputation iteration in R. It combines
    prodNA (by missForest package) and Multiple Imputation Techniques (Mice and missForest in this 
    version) to patching (replaceing) unreliable values in dataset. See help text (TBD) to know more information and 
    procedure of data paching.
    In this version, dataset mayt be constructed by ONLY numeric veriables.
